   <text:p text:style-name="P45">Scrieri</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P41">Demetrescu,Traian</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Autor:Traian_Demetrescu" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T27">https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Autor:Traian_Demetrescu</text:span></text:a></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P67">.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P64"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.ro" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link">https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.ro</text:a><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T30">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">ro</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P39" text:outline-level="1">Aquarele</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Magdalena</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Cnd jalea vntului tomnatic<text:line-break/>Prin desfrunziii arbori trece,<text:line-break/>Tu te gndeti la baluri, doamn, <text:line-break/>Eu m gndesc la soba rece...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Cnd primii fluturi de zpad<text:line-break/>Plutesc n zarea albicioas,<text:line-break/>Tu te gndeti la rochii scumpe,<text:line-break/>Eu m gndesc c-s zdrenuroas...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">i cnd n nopile de iarn<text:line-break/>Cni la clavirul tu, visnd,<text:line-break/>Tu te gndeti c eti iubit, <text:line-break/>Eu m gndesc c-o s m vnd...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Necredincioasa</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Cu trup nalt i mldios, subire<text:line-break/>Ca un salcm crescut abia de-o var,<text:line-break/>Ea pare c sosete dintr&apos;o ar<text:line-break/>ntrevzut n nchipuire...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">C&apos;un gest te farmec de &apos;nfiorare.<text:line-break/>Sau de te-atinge cu matasa rochii,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Sau de-o zreti zmbind, sau de-i vezi ochii<text:line-break/>Primejdioi ca nopile pe mare...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">O! glasul ei!  acorduri de cuvinte, <text:line-break/>Blajin, duios, ca plnsul unor strune, <text:line-break/>Eu l ascult i&apos;l cred, orice mi-ar spune,<text:line-break/>Cum cred btrni &apos;n crile lor sfinte...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Adese-ori m ceart, dar tiu bine<text:line-break/>Mai dulce &apos;n urm o s m desmierde;<text:line-break/>i sufletu-mi n sufletu-i se pierde,<text:line-break/>Precum o raz &apos;n zrile senine...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Ce&apos;mi pas dac, e necredincioas!...<text:line-break/>Urasc-m sau uite-m... tot una...<text:line-break/>Ea m&apos;a iubit,  pstrndu-i tot-de-auna<text:line-break/>Virtutea ei: s fie &apos;n veci frumoas...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">n atelier </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Btrnul s-arat n u<text:line-break/>E grbov sub anii cei grei.<text:line-break/>Stpne, pricepe-mi durerea:<text:line-break/>Furi pnea copiilor mei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Ce lesne sracii ca mine<text:line-break/>Netrebnici pe drumuri s-arunc!<text:line-break/>O via ntreag muncit-am<text:line-break/>i-acum mi iei dreptul la munc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Din braele mele, odat<text:line-break/>Puternice, acum mi rmne<text:line-break/>Doar unul, i-acuma cu-acesta,<text:line-break/>Cer mila ta crud, stpne!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Cnd nu mai sunt bun de nimica,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>M-alungi, i nu ai ndurare!<text:line-break/>i uii ca din braele mele<text:line-break/>Eti astzi puternic i mare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Departe nu-i ceasul din urm<text:line-break/>Cnd zilele mele s-or duce,<text:line-break/>Cci toat rsplata vieii-mi<text:line-break/>E-atta: o groap -o cruce!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Patronul afar-l alung, <text:line-break/>Btrnul sub anii cei grei,<text:line-break/>Cu glasul n lacrimi suspin:<text:line-break/>Furi pnea copiilor mei!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vnztoarea de iluzii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">i.... ntr-o bun diminea,<text:line-break/>Decepia, urt foc,<text:line-break/>Intr-n ora, pe ne-ateptate,<text:line-break/>Strignd: Iluzii de noroc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Iluzii de amor!... Iluzii<text:line-break/>De glorie i tineree!...<text:line-break/>Iluzii mari de sntate!...<text:line-break/>Iluzii dulci de frumusee!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">i marfa asta nesfrit<text:line-break/>Mai mult ca pinea se vindea,<text:line-break/>Cci fiecare-i cumprase<text:line-break/>Iluzia ce urmrea...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Dar un poet, retras de-o parte,<text:line-break/>Zmbea amar spre vnztoare: <text:line-break/>El cunoscuse alt dat<text:line-break/>Pe vecinica amgitoare...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Biletul de noroc </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Iubita mea, care m-neal<text:line-break/>De dou ori pe sptmn.<text:line-break/>Mergea alturea de mine.<text:line-break/>inndu-m de mn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">i m gndeam c-amgitoarea,<text:line-break/>Rznd de visul meu deert,<text:line-break/>Mai dulce o s m srute<text:line-break/>Rugndu-m s-o iert!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">La colul unei strade-nguste,<text:line-break/>De-abia puteai gsi un loc,<text:line-break/>Un vrjitor vindea mulimei<text:line-break/>Bilete de noroc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Am tras i eu la ntmplare<text:line-break/>Biletul meu i l-am pltit;<text:line-break/>n el sta scris aceste vorbe:<text:line-break/>Nu poi fi fericit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">De-atuncea, cnd mi cert iubita<text:line-break/>C m neal pe tot locul,<text:line-break/>Ea m desmiard i mi spune:<text:line-break/>Aa i-e scris norocul!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P62" text:outline-level="3">n ochii lui </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Am o icoan n prete:<text:line-break/>n linii terse-i zugrvit,<text:line-break/>Murind, cu ochii ctre ceruri,<text:line-break/>Divinul rstignit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">La ea se nchinau odat<text:line-break/>Prinii mei... i se rugau;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De-asupra ei, la zile sfinte,<text:line-break/>O candel ardeau...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Eu<text:span text:style-name="T29"> </text:span>am pierdut de mult credina<text:line-break/>i semnul crucei l-am uitat...<text:line-break/>Dar uneori, privind icoana,<text:line-break/>M simt nduioat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">E-att senin i resemnare<text:line-break/>Pe chipul blndului Isus,<text:line-break/>i-atta pietate-artistul<text:line-break/>n ochii lui a pus;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">C-nv, uitndu-m spre dnii:<text:line-break/>Orict cu lumea te-ai lupta<text:line-break/>S-o-nvingi sau s-o urti... mai bine<text:line-break/>S-o tii n veci ierta!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cireele</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P59">Doamnei M. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"> D-mi, fa, cireele!...  Ea tace,<text:line-break/>Dar ochii ei, uimii, i spun:<text:line-break/>Auzi, ciree n Dechemvre!...<text:line-break/>Zu, m biete, eti nebun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"> D-mi, fa, cireele!...  Ea coase<text:line-break/>Cmaa<text:span text:style-name="T29">-</text:span>i prins n ghierghief,<text:line-break/>i-l las-n voie s-aiureze:<text:line-break/>l vede ea c e cu chef.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"> D-mi fa, cireele!...  Ea rde,<text:line-break/>Pricepe fr-a-l ntreba;<text:line-break/>i-acopere cu mna snul,<text:line-break/>optindu-i ruinat: Ba!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Povestea regelui </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P60">n crcium larma se-ntinde,<text:line-break/>Snt mesele pline de lume;<text:line-break/>Iar fetele-mpart tuturora<text:line-break/>Pahare i glume...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P60">Un orb cu o iter-n spate<text:line-break/>S-aeaz pe-un scaun de-o parte;<text:line-break/>i berea se vars-n iroaie<text:line-break/>Din halbele sparte...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P60"> S cnte!... i orbul ncepe,<text:line-break/>i strunele tainice spun,<text:line-break/>Istoria regelui sumbru,<text:line-break/>Uitat i nebun...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P60">O fat frumoas ascult<text:line-break/>i-ntreab: De ce a murit?...<text:line-break/>Iar orbul sfrete povestea:<text:line-break/>Ea nu l-a iubit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Mnchen, 1894</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cerul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Firete, trebuie s fie:<text:line-break/>O armonie, un mister,<text:line-break/>Ce-atrage sufletul spre cer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">n trista mea copilrie, <text:line-break/>Cu paginile ei de plngeri, <text:line-break/>Credeam c ceru-i plin de ngeri...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Credina mea e astzi dus,<text:line-break/>Cu ea i-al visurilor stol, <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i astzi cerul meu e gol!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Dar, ca o tain-n veci nespus,<text:line-break/>Rmas-a vecinicul mister<text:line-break/>Ce-atrage sufletu-mi spre cer!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Doi bogai </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">M-a dus avarul s-mi arate<text:line-break/>ntregul su tezaur,<text:line-break/>i mi-a deschis o lad plin<text:line-break/>Cu aur... aur... aur...<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>Privindu-m cu ochi ironici<text:line-break/>Mi-a zis: Arat-mi mie<text:line-break/>i tu, acum, dac se poate,<text:line-break/>Atta bogie!<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>Atuncia, ca s-mi sting n suflet<text:line-break/>Sarcazmul i amarul,<text:line-break/>i s-i art c de ct mine<text:line-break/>E mai srac avarul;<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>L-am dus grbit spre locuina,<text:line-break/>Spre raiul dragei mele,<text:line-break/>i-am zis avarului: Privete<text:line-break/>Furi printre perdele!<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>El s-a uitat: pe-o pern alb<text:line-break/>Dormea iubita dus,<text:line-break/>i-n jurul ei plutea un farmec<text:line-break/>De linite nespus...<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>Ne-am dus n urm fiecare<text:line-break/>Spre scumpul su tezaur:<text:line-break/>Eu la iubita mea,  Avarul<text:line-break/>Spre lada lui cu aur...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P62" text:outline-level="3">Fata</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"> A cui eti fat?<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> A cui snt nici eu nu-mi dau seam,<text:line-break/>N-am nici surori, nici frai, nici mam,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T29"><text:tab/></text:span>Nici tat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Spun uneori<text:line-break/>Btrnii ce m in de mil,<text:line-break/>Dar nu pricep,  c snt copil<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T29"><text:tab/></text:span>Din flori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"> i cui eti drag? <text:line-break/> Nu-s nimnui, cci snt de vin<text:line-break/>Acei ce m-au lsat strin,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T29"><text:tab/></text:span>i-n veci pribeag...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">Ba... s nu mint:<text:line-break/>Aud c, azi o sptmn,<text:line-break/>M-ar fi vzut, stnd la fntn,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T29"><text:tab/></text:span>Un fiu de prin...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Nostalgii de antichitate </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">n nopile de var, cu limpezi zri de-argint,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Las orele sub visuri nostalgici de se curm:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tresc n alte vremuri, cu veacuri multe-n urm, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Snt dragul unei fete frumoase din Corint.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cnd zilele-s senine colind pe sub arcade,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Admir statui i temple, nu simt cum zboar clipa;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Salut c-un gest molatic pe ceteanu-Antipa,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ce-nir unor tineri prieteni lungi tirade...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Nu snt urt, pe semne, am ochi duioi, statura</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Subire, mldioas, i dinii mei snt perle,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cci azi o curtezan, cu ochi ca dou stele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Privit-a lung la mine c-un zmbet cald pe gur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Asear ntlnit-am, plimbndu-m a lene</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sub bolta fremtoas a unor vechi olivi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O ceat de nemernici, bogai i guralivi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Rznd de neleptul n zdrene  Diogene!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar Cinicul privindu-i, clipind uor din gene,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">I-a risipit c-o vorb, cum risipeti gunoiul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu o sunare,  &apos;n cale-i rostogolind butoiul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-a dus grbit s-asculte vorbind pe Antisithene.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La un banchet, dunzi, ca de-obicei, femeea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ddea prilej de sfad; Lais era cu noi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-avea drept s-o srute pe umerii si goi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cine tia s spuie un vers din Odiseea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">................................................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">................................................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar nopile de var snt scurte... M trezesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cci visurile mele nostalgice se curm...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i din acele vremuri, cu veacuri multe-n urm,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n vremile de astzi revin,  i m-ngrozesc!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Btrnul artist </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-mi cni, s-mi cni un cntec trist,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S stingi din sufletu-mi pojarul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Am zis btrnului artist,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i mi-am umplut cu vin paharul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i el i-a strns sub bra chitara,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-a nceput duios i rar:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cnd soarele apune vara,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Nu te mhni,  rsare iar!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i dac te neal-o fat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Bea un pahar mai mult i taci;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i cat altor fete-ndat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mult mai frumoase, s le placi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Nu-i sfia zadarnic pieptul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De-o suferin trectoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Snt alii care n-au nici dreptul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S plng pentru ce i doare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eu nu tiu alt-fel s descntec</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe cel ce e nenorocit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">................................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sub farmecul acestui cntec,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar am sperat, iar am iubit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Dumani</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eram prieteni vechi, odat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ba din din acelai sat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i pentr-o &apos;mprie &apos;ntreag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Noi nu ne-am fi certat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar ntr-o zi de srbtoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mergnd pe cmp agale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">C-o fat, dintr-un sat aproape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ne-am ntlnit n cale.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">A cui eti, fa?  i-am zis n treact</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ia sti din mers o leac...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">A cui s fiu?  ea ne rspunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">A cui o ti s-mi plac...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Att a trebuit: o vorb,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-un semn cu salba minii, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i dintr-o vorb de muiere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Azi ne mncm ca cinii...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">mpreun</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pornit-au inimi singuratici</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">De tineri i fecioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S dea de urma fericirei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">n lumea asta mare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i fiecare se pierduse</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe-un drum deosebit, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dei spre fericire nu e</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">De ct un drum menit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i singuraticile inimi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">n lunga rtcire.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pierit-au multe... i nici una</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">N-a dat de fericire.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Din stolu-ntreg doar dou inimi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">n goana lor nebun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Au ntlnit-o,  dar acelea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Merseser-mpreun.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ave-Maria (n biserica Sf. tefan) </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ave-Maria... i spre bolta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mreului i trist altar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Fermectorul glas de org</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se-nal ca un plns amar...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n sufletele credincioase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cad notele mngietoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cum peste frunzele de toamn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Amurgul razelor de soare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">ngenunchiat naintea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Crucificatului Hristos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O palid prostituat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Plngea ca un copil duios.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-nmrmurit n durerea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Religioasei aiurri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Prea de veacuri c ateapt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cuvntul ultimei iertri.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Viena, 1894</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Iluzia din urm </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Povestea spune c un tnr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe-un drum grbit mergea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Hei ncotro? &apos;l&apos;ntreab vntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Alerg spre draga mea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">De cnd nu m-a vzut snt veacuri!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ea poate plnge-acum; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O! vntule ai vrea, n fug,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S te ntrec la drum!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ascult, tinere, o clip:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-mi spui, dac se poate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De mai pstrezi cumva iluzii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sau le-ai perdut pe toate?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iluzii?... Sfintele nimicuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-au dus, s-au risipit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Doar una, preuind ct toate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mai am: c snt iubit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Atunci, din drumul tu te-ntoarce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i graba ta o curm </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dac voeti s-i mai rmn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iluzia din urm!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La morg </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Garditii au gsit-o moart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe strad, vnt de frig,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i ctre Morga au pornit-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Fr cociug i fr drig.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Era o biat rtcit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Prostituindu-se pe bani,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu tinereea zdrenuit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Abia la opt-spre-zece ani!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iubitul ei,  poetul palid, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Un vistor frumos i trist,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O-nelegea i o iertase,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Precum pe Magdalena, Krist!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i pe cnd ea la Morga zace</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sub fereastraie i scalpele, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El o ateapt n mansard,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-o caut mereu prin stele...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>ireata</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ea caut n sn scrisoarea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe care-asear i-am cerut-o;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i de o dat-nglbinete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">optindu-mi: Am pierdut-o!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar cnd m uit adnc n ochi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-o vd c minte nu e greu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i linitit o rog atuncea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-o caut eu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lui Pasteur (dup Sully Prrudhomme) </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">n vremile lui Hercul,  titanic faptur, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Natura-nverunat pe om lovea mereu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La rndul su i omul, slbtcit de ur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se-ncumetea la lupt cu cel mai crncen leu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El cucerise astfel, afar&apos; n largul firei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Repaos i putere, de glorie cuprins;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar corpu-i nluntru,  sarcazm al fericirei! </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Fu pe neateptate de un microb nvins.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">ngrozitoarea boal, ce-n snge vars moarte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Lu omului puterea, necontenit s-l poarte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe ci de suferin, de groaz i de chin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar tu, savant ilustru, prin geniul tu divin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Zdrobii vrmau-acesta, menit a fi etern...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n luptele tiinei eti Hercule modern!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Gluma</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Asear i-am trimis priviri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Adnci i rugtoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu mi-ai rspuns cu dulci zmbiri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca razele de soare...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe-o foaie din album i-am scris</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O fraz i un nume;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar tu, rznd ncet, mi-ai zis:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">C nu te-ncrezi n....</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">glume</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tcutele-mi nefericiri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mi le-nlegi acuma...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iubita mea, cu dulci zmbiri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De ce nu-mi crezui...</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">gluma</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Tatl (dup Franois Coppe)</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Acas venea zilnic topit de butur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i biata lui femee rbda orice tortur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Triau de mult vreme. Ea singur, vndut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De mic copil n drumul mizeriei czut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu el nlnuise a traiului povar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i suferea-n tcere btaie i ocar.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Vecinii, cte-o dat, aud biata cum plnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cnd furios brbatul sub pumni spinarea-i frnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-o chinuete pn se-nmoaie de-oboseal; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Apoi se face-o larg tcere mormntal.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar ntr-o zi de iarn, cnd aspra srcie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Preface o secund n crud vecinicie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i gura cere pine i nu-i o frmitur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Femeea nate-n chinuri o slab creatur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Srman copil! ce dulce i bun i-ar fi soarta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Nscnd de i-ar deschide spre somnul morei poarta!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Brbatul vine iari beat ntr-o zi, cum face</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n tot-d&apos;a-una; ns e potolit i tace...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Nu mai ridic mna nevasta iar s geam</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sub lovituri puternici; acuma ea e mam!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i, zmbitor, alturi de leagn se aeaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i mngie copilul ce doarme i viseaz...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Femeea cum l vede, cu ochii ari de ur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">ntoarce ctre dnsul o rea cuttur;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Deprins cu btaia l-ntreab i rnjete:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Azi nu m bai! Ia spune-mi, ce lucru te oprete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eu te atept!.. Hai, vino... i d-mi!... Iar imbecilul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Rspunde-ncet: Mi-e fric s nu detept copilul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Clugrul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Clugrul din vechiul schit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O zi la el ne-a gzduit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i de-ale lumii mi-a vorbit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar cnd s plec, l-am ntrebat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ce soart rea te-a ndrumat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S cai un loc printre sihatrii?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El mi-a rspuns: Doi ochi albatri!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Clugarul din vechiul schit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De-un dor ascuns a-nebunit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Atunci tovarii lui buni</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">ntr-un ospiciu l-au lsat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">L-am revzut, l-am ntrebat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ce te-a adus printre nebuni?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eu te tiam printre sihatri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El mi-a rspuns: Doi ochi albatri!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Zdrenurosul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu nu m poi iubi pe mine:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu eti frumoas, eu... frumos;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar tu eti bine mbrcat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i eu snt zdrenuros.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu n-o s te opreti o clip</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Durerea mea s mi-o asculi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu treci n faietonu-i mndru,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eu prin noroi, descul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i n-o s-mi fie dat norocul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Odat s te chiem pe nume:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu-mi pari din visuri c faci parte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe cnd eu snt din lume.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Oh, cerul este plin de soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pmntu-i plin de frumusee...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar pentru ce nu-i fericit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">O inim sub zdrene?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Muncitorilor</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Vor rsri, ca nite astre,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Senine lumi cu oameni noi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-n vremile acele sfinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pmntul poate va fi raiu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Vor rsuna mai dulci cuvinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n cntecile lor de Maiu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:span text:style-name="T20">Ct o via</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ne-am ntlnit pe-o vreme trist,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i, plini de ploaie i noroi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu-ncredere ne-am luat de mn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pornind spre cas amndo.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n camer un frig de moarte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ea m-a-ntrebat din ochi: rmi? </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-am mprit, strini i singuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Acelai rece cptiu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i unul altuia povestea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Vieei noastre ne-am optit:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ea tot-d&apos;a-una neiubit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eu tot-d&apos;a-una neiubit...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">C-o dureroas voluptate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La sn ca doi copii ne-am strns,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-n noaptea aceea, ct o via,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Am plns... i ne-am iubit... i am plns...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ciobanii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ciobanii stau n jurul vetrei </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Afar negur i moin </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">M, Miule, grete unul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ce stai aa?, ia zi o doin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Hei!.. de-asta-i arde lui acuma!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El singur doar i tie halul... </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sfios i necjit rspunde: </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu ce s cnt?... c n-am cavalul...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar unde-i, m? - Unde s fie?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">L-a frnt boieru pe spinare-mi; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar i eu-n gndul meu, de ciud,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">I-am tras o-njurtur, barem!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Din Bavaria </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei cnt... Danul lor se-ntinde<text:line-break/>Sub umbra ulmului btrn,<text:line-break/>Iar alii beau i pe genunche<text:line-break/>i strng iubitele la sn.<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>iganii tlmcesc pe strune<text:line-break/>Din cnteci vechi poveti de dor,<text:line-break/>i sub mestrele arcuuri<text:line-break/>Plng inimile tuturor...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P56">Bavaria e plin toat<text:line-break/>De muni, de lacuri, de femei,<text:line-break/>i nu-i drgu s nu-i aib<text:line-break/>Drguul ei.<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>Strin cnd m-au vzut pe mine<text:line-break/>C trec pribeag i singur lacu,<text:line-break/>Toi m-au privit duios, optindu-i:<text:line-break/>Sracu!<text:line-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Thumsee, 1894</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Aleluia</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Egalitate! Fraternitate!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se vaiet prin arbori vntul...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i pare-un glas pierdut pe stradt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ce cnt-a morei serenad:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">V-acopere pe toi pmntul...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Nimic!... rmne-n veci cuvntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Din a vieei trist sfad!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se vaiet prin arbori vntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i pare-un glas pierdut pe strad...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ai neles deznodmntul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca ntr-o stranie balad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-adun oasele grmad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ne face frai pe toi mormntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se vaiet prin arbori vntul...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Privind Alpii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Te-nal cu gndirea pe culmile senine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i sufletu-i rmie acolo tot-d&apos;a-una.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tcut i singuratic,  precum n haos luna,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Departe de-ale lunei sarcazme i suspine...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n sus, n sus spre largul tcerilor eterne</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">E singurul refugiu de pace i uitare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu ct eti mai departe de oameni e mai mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i linitea, ce blnd pe fruntea ta s-aterne...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar jos... aceleai patimi n veci o s rmn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-arunce printre oameni i vrajb i minciuni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Aceai comedie jucat de nebuni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sfritul tot acelai: o mn de rn...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Thumsee, 1894</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Din glasul tu </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ai stat o sear, lng mine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe-o banc, i-am vorbit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De cte-n lun i n stele </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-apoi ne-am desprit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Firete, cine ine minte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Aceea ce-a fost ieri?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O sear trece i se uit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca multe alte seri...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar mie mi-ai rmas n suflet</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O fericire rar:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ceva din glasul tu, mai dulce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca linitea de sear...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Farmec</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Am poposit o noapte, vere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La o crciumreas-n sat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i, arz-o focu de muiere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe semne c m-a fermecat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Din bun cretin m-nchin cu stnga,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i tot la ea m-ai ndruma;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i nu mi-e c i-am lsat punga,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar i-am lsat i inima...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe lacul Thum </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Alunec, n luntre, pe lac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i umbra pe ap s-aterne;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n juru-ne Alpii-i desfac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Priveliti eterne.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i cerbii pe rpe se suie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Aiurea pierzndu-se-n cete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe mal stau glume s-i spuie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Grmad de fete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mi-e sufletul plin de uimire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-mi zic iar ce vecinic mi zic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n lume e numai iubire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar restul  nimic!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Departe, o iter plnge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Accente nebune de patimi; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n sufletu-mi singur se strnge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">O lume de lacrimi...</text:span><text:line-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Reichenhall, 1894</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Idil</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Duminic ne-am dat cuvntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">S ne-ntlnim, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cci ne-am jurat n toat viaa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">S ne iubim.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">A mea a fost ntia oar...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i dracului</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-a dat c n-are s mai fie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">A nimnui.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Duminic am ateptat-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar n-a venit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Am stat pe gnduri toat ziua,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i n-am dormit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La crcium, un vechiu prieten</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mi-a spus curat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O vorb ce m-a scos din fire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">M-a-ntunecat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Azi noapte i-am btut n u,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i mi-a deschis;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">A vrut s mi s-arunce-n brae, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Nimic n-am zis.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De piept am luat-o, ca o fiar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i am trt-o;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar... arma mi-a czut din mn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">N-am omort-o!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Frunze de toamn </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pic frunzele de toamn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Scuturate de furtun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i picnd ca o ninsoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Fac pmntului cunun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Melancolic, prin fereastr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Mi-aruuc ochii ctre ele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i privindu-le le-asamn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu iluziile mele...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Dou drumuri </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Te-am ntlnit n drumul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Din ntmplare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu te grbeai spre fericire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eu rtceam ctre uitare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar m-ai oprit cu un cuvnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i c-o zmbire;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">M-ai luat alturea de tine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe calea ctre fericire...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Azi te ursc... i-mi caut drumul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">n urma ta;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Tu eti aiurea fericit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe cnd eu nu mai pot uita...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntreul de strad</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">ntr-un ora, din ntmplare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Venise-un cntre de strad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i dintr-o iter duioas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cnta aceast serenad:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iubii-v! viaa trece</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca adierea unei seri;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n inimile iubitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">E cald, senin,  snt primveri!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Atunci, bcanii auzindu-l,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">L-au dat afar din ora;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar unul dintre ei rostit-a:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe legea mea! e un punga!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Lng teghele, toat ziua,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca vai de lume ne trudim,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S strngem ban cu ban, grmad, -</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Noi n-avem vreme s iubim!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Femeile au plns de mila</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Acelui cntre gonit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cci inimile lor duioase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La viersul lui s-au nclzit...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i s-au rugat s-l readuc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-i dea un ban, un adpost;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">E zdrenuros, e mort de foame</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i e strin!  dar chip n-a fost!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n inimile tineri ns</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Rmas-a cntecul neters...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i dup cum aud pe unii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cam astfel treburile-au mers:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Bcanii-au strns-n toat viaa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ban lng ban, cu mare pre;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe cnd nevestele urmat-au</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Povaa-acelui cntre.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O minune </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">ranii-mi spun, cinstii la vorb,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">C-s oameni drepi i buni:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pdurea asta e vestit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Vestit n minuni!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Atia suferinzi fcut-a</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De via s-aib parte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cnd se credeau ajuni aproape</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De ne-ndurata moarte.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Din multe locuri deprtate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Vin oameni ca s-o vaz, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i de mndreea-i fr seamn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Adnc se minuneaz!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ascult i-ncep s cred ca dnii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Minunile aceste, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cum un copil se-nfioreaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De orice i ce poveste.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar ai voi s-ntreb pe unul, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El singur doar mi-o spune, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dac-ar putea ca s mai fac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pdurea o minune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-mi risipeasc stolul negru</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De nopi i zile rele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i s-mi redea nemrginitul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iluziilor mele!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Solca, 1895</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Doi beivi </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">M mbtaser de privirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De gura unei dulci femei, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i, beat, m ntorceam acas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe drumul strejuit de tei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La o rspnte-mi iese-n cale.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Un om necunoscut, strin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Era tot beat,  dar beat, sracul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">De suferine si de vin.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ne-am dat n vorb despre multe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca nite linitii drumei;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i ne-am mrturisit n fine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Din ce pricin sntem bei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eti beat,  mi-a zis el filosofic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">De fericire, de senin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Curnd o s le-neci, ca mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe toate-n lacrime i-n vin!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Copii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">E un copil! E o copil!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Snt amndoi copii!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iubirea lor e o idil,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cum snt prin poezii...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Furii se ntlnesc adese,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i el i reciteaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sonete din</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">Musset</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">culese;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ea tace i ofteaz...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El cu o vorb mintea-i fur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-o farmec, iretul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar se lovete peste gur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">C i-a optit secretul...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu oapte calde i timide</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iubirea lor i-o-ngn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar ntlnirea lor se-nchide</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">C-o strngere de mn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se hotrsc n ziua-a dou</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">S se revad iari...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iubirea lor e vecinic nou,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">De i snt vechi tovari.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i setea patimei aprins</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Din ochi li se revars:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ea pleac de durere-nvins,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">El cu simirea ars!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iubirea lor e o idil,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cum snt prin poezii:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">El un copil! Ea o copil!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Snt amndoi copii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Unei iubite </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">M-mbat glasul ei blajin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i prul ei lsat pe spate...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ea m iubete ca pe un frate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ca pe-un copil orfan, strin.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se uit-n ochii-mi cnd suspin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">M ceart-ades cu buntate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">M-mbat glasul ei blajin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i prul ei lsat pe spate...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">n faa-i stau, tcut, senin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i uit de-a vieei rutate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cnd mnile-i, ca inspirate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Scot din clavir un plns divin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">M-mbat glasul ei blajin...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Aceleai locuri </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Le recunosc aceste locuri:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Crrile erpuitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Te duc sub tainici boli de frunze,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Te-ascund de lume i de soare...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Un lin izvor i face cale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Pe lng irul de anini,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar dintr-un parc aduce vntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Miros de salcie i crini.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Iar seara-n amurgit, pe vale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">S-aude clopotul din sat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">nflorind nemrginirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">C-un sunet vag i deprtat...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Le recunosc aceste locuri, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i totui parc mi s-arat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Aa strine... Le lipsete:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Inima mea de alt dat...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Vistorul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T10">Am rtcit pe multe drumuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i-n lunga-mi rtcire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Visam s ntlnesc o umbr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Ce-i zice: Fericire.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T22"></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Dar n-am gsit-o nicirea </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Deunzi, obosit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">ntr-o pdure fremtoas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O clip m-am oprit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Sub un copac, btrn ca mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">O fat i-un biat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se srutau soptindu-i oapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Cu glasul ngnat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i cnd s plec, biatul parc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Se nclin spre ea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Zicndu-i blnd: O, tu, iubito;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Eti fericirea mea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Am tresrit... i-n clipa-aceia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">C-o repede privire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">M-am i ntors s vd cum este</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Visata fericire?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Era o fat cum snt multe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Prin sate i orae:</te